direction: right

User: External User {
  shape: person
}

Cloud: AWS {
  CloudFront: Amazon CloudFront {
    OAC: Origin Access Control {
      style: { stroke: "#FF4F8B" }
    }
    style: { stroke: "#FF9900"; stroke-width: 2 }
  }

  S3: Private Assets Bucket {
    shape: cylinder
    style: { stroke: "#3F7E44" }
    
    Lifecycle: Lifecycle Rules {
      label: "Standard-IA (30d)\nGlacier (60d)"
    }
  }
}

User -> Cloud.CloudFront: HTTPS Request
Cloud.CloudFront.OAC -> Cloud.S3: Signed Request (SigV4)
Cloud.S3 -> Cloud.CloudFront: Returns Object
Cloud.CloudFront -> User: Delivers Content
